hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有非齐次系统
$$\frac{d\mathbf{x}}{dt}=A(t)\mathbf{x}+\mathbf{g}(t),\quad
A(t)=\begin{pmatrix}\alpha  \gamma t\\0  \alpha\end{pmatrix},\;
\mathbf{g}(t)=\begin{pmatrix}0\\\delta e^{\alpha t}\end{pmatrix}.$$
1.  求齐次系统的基本矩阵 $\Phi(t)$。可以验证
$$x^{(1)}(t)=\begin{pmatrix}e^{\alpha t}\\0\end{pmatrix},\quad
x^{(2)}(t)=\begin{pmatrix}\frac{\gamma\,t^2}{2}e^{\alpha t}\\e^{\alpha t}\end{pmatrix}$$
是线性无关的解，因此
$$\Phi(t)=\begin{pmatrix}e^{\alpha t}  \frac{\gamma\,t^2}{2}e^{\alpha t}\\0  e^{\alpha t}\end{pmatrix} 
=e^{\alpha t}\begin{pmatrix}1  \frac{\gamma t^2}{2}\\0  1\end{pmatrix}.$$
2.  计算 $\Phi^{-1}(t)$：
$$\Phi^{-1}(t)=e^{-\alpha t}\begin{pmatrix}1  -\frac{\gamma t^2}{2}\\0  1\end{pmatrix}.$$
3.  根据常数变易法，一个特解是
$$\mathbf{x}_p(t)=\Phi(t)\int\Phi^{-1}(s)\,\mathbf{g}(s)\,ds.$$
我们有
$$\Phi^{-1}(s)\,\mathbf{g}(s)
=e^{-\alpha s}\begin{pmatrix}1  -\frac{\gamma s^2}{2}\\0  1\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}0\\\delta e^{\alpha s}\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}-\frac{\gamma\delta\,s^2}{2}\\\delta\end{pmatrix},$$
所以
$$\int\Phi^{-1}(s)\,\mathbf{g}(s)\,ds
=\begin{pmatrix}-\frac{\gamma\delta}{2}\int s^2\,ds\\\int\delta\,ds\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}-\frac{\gamma\delta\,s^3}{6}\\\delta\,s\end{pmatrix}
\Biggr|_{0}^{t}
=\begin{pmatrix}-\frac{\gamma\delta\,t^3}{6}\\\delta\,t\end{pmatrix}.$$
因此
$$\mathbf{x}_p(t)
=\begin{pmatrix}e^{\alpha t}  \frac{\gamma\,t^2}{2}e^{\alpha t}\\0  e^{\alpha t}\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}-\frac{\gamma\delta\,t^3}{6}\\\delta\,t\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}\frac{\gamma\delta\,t^3}{3}e^{\alpha t}\\\delta\,t\,e^{\alpha t}\end{pmatrix}.$$
